org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.coord.subprocess
Interface IAeSpCoordinating

All Superinterfaces:
IAeCoordinating
All Known Subinterfaces:
IAeSpCoordinator, IAeSpParticipant
All Known Implementing Classes:
AeSpCoordinator, AeSpParticipant
public interface IAeSpCoordinating
extends IAeCoordinating

Interface indicating a AE subprocess protocol type coordinating activity. The AE subprocess protocol is loosely based on Business Agreement protocol described in the BPEL-4WS 1.1, appendix C.
